userParam.name: The ProteoRed MIAPE Extractor tool is a standalone tool that allows: to obtain graphical representations of qualitative information from MIAPE MSI documents; to automatically create MIAPE compliant reports from your standard data files (PRIDE XML, mzML, mzIdentML) and others (XTandem output xml), storing these reports in the ProteoRed MIAPE repository; to export your MIAPE-compliant reports to standard data files (currently to PRIDE XML).
